de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface FaultPropagation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FaultPropagationImpl

    public interface FaultPropagation
extends ElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Fault Propagation'. Specifies how the state of the inputs transfers to the outputs. An arbitrary Boolean logic can be created.

    The following features are supported:

    • Output State
    • Logic
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getFaultPropagation()
